span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#333333\"><img alt=\"https://cdn.mediamart.vn/images/Upload/images/3(702).jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.mediamart.vn/images/Upload/images/3(702).jpg\" style=\"height:533px; width:800px\" /></span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Helvetica&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:black\">R&otilde; Khung H&igrave;nh, Mượt Chuyển Động</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">C&ocirc;ng Nghệ Motion Xcelerator&nbsp;- Trong c&aacute;c ph&acirc;n cảnh đua xe hoặc rượt đuổi, c&aacute;c khung h&igrave;nh thay đổi li&ecirc;n tục dễ dẫn đến hiện tượng &quot;b&oacute;ng ma&quot; tr&ecirc;n m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh. C&ocirc;ng nghệ Motion Xcelerator sẽ tự động bổ sung th&ecirc;m khung h&igrave;nh để nội dung r&otilde; n&eacute;t v&agrave; mượt m&agrave; hơn tr&ecirc;n chiếc&nbsp;<a href=\"https://mediamart.vn/tivi-samsung?f=smart-tv\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#007bff\">Smart tivi</span></a>&nbsp;n&agrave;y.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left\"><span style=\"font-size:14px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#333333\"><img alt=\"https://cdn.mediamart.vn/images/Upload/images/2(838).jpg\" src=\"http